body:
I build the quantization tools on tensorflow v0.11.0 https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/v0.11.0. 
The graph pb file and the sh file to run the quantization process is included in 
[quantize_graph.zip](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/856868/quantize_graph.zip). 
Thanks.
